      "text": "Corticosteroids\n+/-\nAzathioprine\nManage complications, see:\nAscites\n,\nSBP\nUpper gastrointestinal bleed\nHepatorenal syndrome\nHepatic encephalopathy\nUltimately, may require transplant\nHepatology/Gastroenterology consult should be made",
